  ('bookkeeper-moex-00933', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-107-12108af6', 'sub-bookkeeper-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '某一負債預期將於資產負債表日後十二個月內到期清償，倘若該負債於資產負債表日後至通過財務報表 前已完成長期性之再融資或重新安排付款協議時，該負債應列於何類別？', '["流動負債", "長期負債", "負債準備", "應付公司債"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f48c0160167d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "60479f881885", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107180", "c": "602", "s": "1302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "記帳相關法規概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('bookkeeper-moex-00934', 'bookkeeper', 'bookkeeper-moex-107-12108af6', 'sub-bookkeeper-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '營利事業收到股東依其出資比例捐贈的資產時，該項受贈資產應如何認列？', '["其他收入", "遞延收入", "其他權益", "資本公積"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:29:25+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f48c0160167d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "60479f881885", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107180", "c": "602", "s": "1302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "記帳相關法規概要", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "bookkeeper", "db_exam_id": "bookkeeper"}'::jsonb, NULL),
